<blockquote style=3D"margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:12.0pt">On 27 Aug 2025, at 4:3=
0<span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">=E2=80=AF</span>PM=
, Grant Metson &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz">Grant.Metson@=
tower.co.nz</a>&gt; wrote:<o:p></o:p></p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<blockquote style=3D"margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt">
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-se=
rif">=EF=BB=BF</span> <o:p>
</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hi Rafaella,</span><=
o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I can give you a mor=
e comprehensive update on Friday. But for now =E2=80=93 I can briefly respon=
d as below:</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Your Claims manager w=
ill update you on the content=E2=80=99s aspect of your claim. I have no know=
ledge or jurisdiction on the contents claim. However, I will follow up with y=
our claims manager for that contents side
 of things on Friday when I=E2=80=99m back in the office.</span><o:p></o:p><=
/p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Re =E2=80=93 your ow=
n assessment =E2=80=93 you are welcome to book that in very soon. I would re=
commend that we meet again at your home early next week before you do that. I=
t would be very beneficial to meet onsite again
 and have a face-to-face update on the claim=E2=80=99s progression.</span><o=
:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As you know we have i=
nspected the exterior wall cavities and have found some smoke contamination i=
n some isolated areas =E2=80=93 so we will explore that further to ensure th=
at it is included in the scope of work.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I=E2=80=99m travelli=
ng all day tomorrow =E2=80=93 but will endeavor to provide you with a more c=
omprehensive update on Friday.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please let me know i=
f you would like to book a site meeting in for next week.</span><o:p></o:p><=
/p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regards,</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant. </span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
