if">I look forward to your response addressing the points above.</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
<p><span style=3D"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-ser=
if">Kind regards,<br>
Rafaella</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<div class=3D"MsoNormal" align=3D"center" style=3D"text-align:center">
<hr size=3D"1" width=3D"100%" align=3D"center">
</div>
<p><span style=3D"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-ser=
if">Let me know if you want to attach the policy wording or include any refe=
rences to specific clauses.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<blockquote style=3D"margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt">
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">On 22 Jul 2025, at 12:19<span style=3D"font-family:&q=
uot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">=E2=80=AF</span>PM, Grant Metson &lt;<a href=3D"=
mailto:Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz">Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz</a>&gt; wrote:<o:p=
></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good afternoon Rafae=
lla,</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I wanted to take the=
 time to thank you very much for meeting with Chris, David and myself at you=
r place this afternoon. It was much appreciated.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I felt that the meet=
ing was very productive and positive as we all discussed the next steps and h=
ave agreed on the claim=E2=80=99s progression process moving forward.</span>=
<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I would like to re-c=
onfirm the next steps we agreed to in writing, and share with all as below:<=
/span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0in" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso=
-list:l2 level1 lfo5">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Asset Restore to attend site as soon as pos=
sible and complete the process of assessing and cataloging the contents for t=
he response of the contents claim. After assessment the contents which are c=
ategorised as a total loss will
 be removed from site.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" s=
tyle=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo5">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Asset Restore to strip out the property of a=
ny fire or smoke damaged linings or other non-structural items. This will en=
able a clear and clean structural assessment to be undertaken, from which we=
 will produce a scope of works
 for the repairs required.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagra=
ph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo5">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Once we have a scope of works completed =E2=
=80=93 we will share this with you to approve before we submit to our repair=
 panel for tendering.</span><o:p></o:p></li></ol>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Confirming that you h=
ave notified us of the access code to be 1106.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We will keep you upd=
ated on the above process and communicate with you as we move through the ab=
ove steps.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have spoken with b=
oth our Motor and our Claims Team Leaders, and they have said that the items=
 you have enquired about are very unlikely to be affected by the fire given t=
heir location with respect to the
 proximity of the fire. I do understand that you would like to be 100% certa=
in that the lithium batteries in these items have not been affected from the=
 fire. The standard process in this situation is that you can undertake any t=
esting of any of your items
 which you wish to, to obtain test results or a report which your insurer ca=
n consider for inclusion in your claims. If the test results prove any damag=
e or loss to these items from the fire =E2=80=93 then your insurer will cons=
ider them within your claim.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">For contents items -=
 please direct your enquiries to<span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;=
</span><a href=3D"mailto:claims@tower.co.nz"><span style=3D"color:#467886">c=
laims@tower.co.nz</span></a></span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As you do not yet ha=
ve a motor claim with Tower from this event =E2=80=93 you can also send any m=
otor reports to<a href=3D"mailto:claims@tower.co.nz"><span style=3D"color:#4=
67886">claims@tower.co.nz</span></a><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&n=
bsp;</span>and
 they will respond accordingly.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you again and I=
 strongly encourage you to call me on the number below with any concerns tha=
t you have with the process of the claim progression.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">All the best,</span>=
<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
